# Spartan UI + Tailwind CSS

## UI Stack

- **Components**: Spartan UI (headless, CDK-based primitives)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v3.4.x utility classes
- **NO Angular Material** — never import `@angular/material/*`

> **Important**: Utilitzem Tailwind CSS v3, NO v4. Veure `docs/TAILWIND_VERSION.md` per detalls.

## Theming

### CSS Setup (Tailwind v3)

```scss
// apps/dashboard/src/styles.scss
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

:root {
  --colla-primary: #1B5E20;
  --colla-secondary: #FDD835;
  --colla-text-on-primary: #FFFFFF;
}
```

### Tailwind Config

```javascript
// tailwind.config.js (arrel del projecte)
module.exports = {
  content: [
    './apps/dashboard/src/**/*.{html,ts}',
    './apps/pwa/src/**/*.{html,ts}',
